  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Chiropractic Clinic Assistant",
  "description": "<p>Reform Chiropractic in Serangoon is looking for a friendly, motivated individual to join our team. Our clinic hours are Tuesday 2pm - 7pm, Wednesday to Friday 9am - 7pm (with a lunch break from 1pm - 3pm), and Saturday 9am - 1pm. Assistants are required to arrive 30 minutes before opening to help clean and prepare the clinic for the day.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Communicate directly with patients to handle inquiries, manage bookings, and schedule appointments efficiently</li><li>Operate the chiropractic front desk system to schedule appointments and process invoicing accurately</li><li>Maintain clinic cleanliness by vacuuming, mopping, and cleaning the washroom on a rotating schedule with staff</li><li>Support doctors by managing patient flow smoothly during clinic hours</li><li>Teach patients simple exercises such as stretching and foam rolling to support their health and recovery, using training provided</li><li>Prepare patients for treatment by setting up traction machines or blocks as directed</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Previous experience in chiropractic or pain management clinics to enhance patient support</li><li>Knowledge of exercises related to health and well-being, including stretching and foam rolling</li><li>Friendly and approachable communication style to create a welcoming environment</li><li>Willingness to learn new skills and clinic procedures</li><li>Interest in general health and well-being to engage effectively with patients</li><li>Proficiency with technology to manage scheduling and invoicing systems</li><li>Ability to communicate in Mandarin is a plus due to the local community language context</li></ul>",
